abstract: Exuberant over the candidates’ performances, he continued his tour through the West.
snippet: Exuberant over the candidates’ performances, he continued his tour through the West.
lead_paragraph: LAS VEGAS — Flying to Las Vegas from Phoenix on Wednesday night on Air Force One, President Trump was glued to the Democratic presidential primary debate.

abstract: Elizabeth Warren enters the final stretch before Saturday's Nevada Democratic caucus with a new and enviable but nonetheless critical mission: capitalizing on a standout performance during Wednesday's presidential debate.
snippet: Elizabeth Warren enters the final stretch before Saturday's Nevada Democratic caucus with a new and enviable but nonetheless critical mission: capitalizing on a standout performance during Wednesday's presidential debate.
lead_paragraph: WASHINGTON — Elizabeth Warren enters the final stretch before Saturday's Nevada Democratic caucus with a new and enviable but nonetheless critical mission: capitalizing on a standout performance during Wednesday's presidential debate.
headline_main: Warren's Next Challenge: Maintain Post-Debate Momentum
headline_print_headline: Warren's Next Challenge: Maintain Post-Debate Momentum

abstract: His aura suddenly shattered, a defiant Michael Bloomberg sent a pointed message Thursday to a political world grappling with his underwhelming presidential debate debut: He's not going away.
snippet: His aura suddenly shattered, a defiant Michael Bloomberg sent a pointed message Thursday to a political world grappling with his underwhelming presidential debate debut: He's not going away.
lead_paragraph: SALT LAKE CITY — His aura suddenly shattered, a defiant Michael Bloomberg sent a pointed message Thursday to a political world grappling with his underwhelming presidential debate debut: He's not going away.
headline_main: Wounded but Defiant, Bloomberg Promises to Keep Fighting
headline_print_headline: Wounded but Defiant, Bloomberg Promises to Keep Fighting

abstract: Relishing in Democrats' jumbled primary in the wake of a fractious debate, President Donald Trump offered stinging criticism of his rivals as he sought to take advantage of the moment.
snippet: Relishing in Democrats' jumbled primary in the wake of a fractious debate, President Donald Trump offered stinging criticism of his rivals as he sought to take advantage of the moment.
lead_paragraph: COLORADO SPRINGS, Colo. — Relishing in Democrats' jumbled primary in the wake of a fractious debate, President Donald Trump offered stinging criticism of his rivals as he sought to take advantage of the moment.
headline_main: Trump Savoring Scrambled Dem Race, Bloomberg's Debate Debut
headline_print_headline: Trump Savoring Scrambled Dem Race, Bloomberg's Debate Debut

abstract: Dems should be talking about financialization and fraud.
snippet: Dems should be talking about financialization and fraud.
lead_paragraph: Wednesday’s Democratic debate was far more informative than previous debates. What we learned, in particular, was that as a presidential candidate, Michael Bloomberg is a great businessman — and that Elizabeth Warren remains a force to be reckoned with.

abstract: A classified briefing to House members is said to have angered the president, who complained that Democrats would “weaponize” the disclosure.
snippet: A classified briefing to House members is said to have angered the president, who complained that Democrats would “weaponize” the disclosure.
lead_paragraph: WASHINGTON — Intelligence officials warned House lawmakers last week that Russia was interfering in the 2020 campaign to try to get President Trump re-elected, five people familiar with the matter said, a disclosure to Congress that angered Mr. Trump, who complained that Democrats would use it against him.

abstract: The notion of banning fracking is dividing the Democrats running for president and increasingly dividing Democrats in the presidential battleground state of Pennsylvania, where fracking has vaulted it to the No. 2 natural gas producer behind Texas.
